<HEAD>China Stops Live Coverage by American Television</HEAD>
<HEAD>With PM-China, Bjt</HEAD>
<HEAD>Eds: INSERTS 2 grafs after 9th graf, `Mr. Gorbachev...' to UPDATE
with CNN seeking permission to restore broadcasts. Picks up 10th graf pvs,
